              Ella Rises exists to empower young women to pursue higher education by surrounding them with meaningful mentorship,
              high-impact experiences, and a community that celebrates who they are. Through multicultural programming rooted in
              <strong>mariachi</strong> and hands-on <strong>STEAM</strong> learning, students build confidence, learn practical skills,
              and discover pathways to college and career goals they can truly see themselves achieving.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #333; margin: 0;">
              Our programs combine music, culture, and real-world exploration to foster leadership, academic motivation, and a sense of
              belonging. Whether a student is picking up an instrument for the first time or building a project in a workshop, Ella Rises
              helps her grow her voice, expand her vision, and take the next step toward a bright future.
            </p>
